reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits Only One Model
reviews.reviewText: This case is made especially for the Samsung Galaxy S23 FE and is available in a variety of colors to fit your style. Although it isn't bulky, it features the right cuts to ensure that, even with the case on, your phone's buttons and camera function as designed.According to the manufacturer, the waterproof cover can protect the phone from water up to six feet deep. This gives me comfort knowing that my phone would be protected in the event of a crisis, even though I'm not going to try it. I've lost a phone before after being thrown into a pool while carrying it in my pocket.It is not difficult to put on or take off the case, even if it fits the phone snugly. I know it's safe even if I drop it because it has shock absorption. It includes a built-in screen protector, so I don't need to buy one separately, and it can be charged on my wireless charger with the case on. This is reasonably priced, well-made, functional, and protects my phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Pros: Case seems very well made. Sturdy. Touch screen and fingerprint unlock still works well with built in screen protector. Easy to put on phone. I have full confidence it will protect my phone from impacts olif dropped. I have no intention of taking the risk to test its waterproof capabilities.Cons: it's much bulkier than I expected but I still keep it. However, I cannot use my charging cable with it (Type C) as the protective housing is too thick to fit. Fortunately, the cable that came with my phone will work but it's much shorter, but I need one for the car as well. I have to buy new cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great case for the price
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this case for my Galaxy S24+ Ultra. I really enjoy how the case snaps together, creating an air tight feel. I wasn't sure how good the quality would be given the price but I was pleasantly surprised when I started using it. It's been about 2 weeks utilizing this new case and my only negative feedback would be the S-Pen is a little hard to get to while in the case but given I rarely use the S-Pen, this isn't a big deal.The case protects my phone from drops which gives me peace of mind if I accidently drop / or it falls. The orange tab near the charger is also a pretty clever design. You can switch it over to give a water tight connection as needed. Very cool. The charging port is also covered so debris / grime doesn't get inside. For the price, I absolutely love this case. Definitely recommend purchasing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality Case with a perfect fit!
reviews.reviewText: Bought this case for the new Galaxy S24+ and it is a perfect fit. I waited in the past for BodyGlove to roll out their own protective cases but this one is of higher quality than theirs. Super easy installation and fingerprint sensor is still very responsive! The seal around the phone is great and when the charging port is covered and the waterproofing is covering the microphone, no water is able to seap through. Highly recommend this case for S24+

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ultimate Peace of Mind for Galaxy S24 Ultra Owners
reviews.reviewText: Owning the Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra Waterproof Case has given me ultimate peace of mind. Its 360° full-body protection ensures that my device is safe from all angles, whether it’s water, dust, or shock. The built-in lens and screen protector are features that have significantly enhanced my user experience, maintaining the pristine condition of my phone’s display and camera. The heavy-duty protective capabilities of this case do not compromise the phone’s functionality, which is a significant advantage. The precision cutouts and the responsive nature of the built-in protectors make using my Galaxy S24 Ultra as seamless as if it weren’t encased at all. The sleek black design is just the cherry on top, providing a stylish yet formidable shield against any adversities. This case is a perfect blend of protection, functionality, and style, making it an indispensable accessory for Galaxy S24 Ultra users.
